            <title>[KAFKA-13396] kafka-topics.sh --create should not require the partitions/replication-factor argument</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-13396</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
